item.title: Don't Sweat Buying Me The Nice Stuff 😉
item.description: When it comes to nice things – like you – I like them too. Now, you don’t have to go through a difficult time trying to figure out what you want to buy for me 😁. Books I’m an avid reader. My reading taste ranges from romantic, adventure, biographies up to technical and non-technical all the way to any genre that will pique my interest. I read quite a lot. Now, in no particular order, here is a list of books I’d like to read:
